text: Let's Go Dating (Chinese: 我们去相亲) is a variety programme produced by Mediacorp Channel 8. It is hosted by a rotating team of presenters composed of two from a team of the four hosts Youyi, Wang Weiliang, Tosh Zhang and Teddy Tang. ==See also== *Mediacorp Channel 8 ==References== Category:2017 Singaporean television series debuts Category:2017 Singaporean television series endings Category:Channel 8 (Singapore) original programming
title: Let's Go Dating
